parameters: This is my room where you'll be working.

So, first off, I'd like to ask you to do some simple
housework.
Could you please clean my room?
Hold on, in this place, I am the master.
Please use honorifics and respectful language.
Are there any items I should not touch while cleaning?
Well, I'd prefer you not to touch my desk.

There are valuable things on it, and it would be a problem
if they were knocked over.

Other than that, there's nothing in particular. I'll be
doing my work, so don't mind me and go ahead with the
cleaning.

(Just the area around the desk left... I mustn't touch the
desk itself.)
I told you not to touch the desk, didn't I!
Master...! I did not touch the desk...!
Then why did it fall! I haven't touched it either!

You must have touched it without realizing! It's your fault
it's broken!

(Did I touch it without noticing...? But I can't prove that
I definitely didn't...)

What are you going to do about this! It was a very valuable
item!
Useless servant! You need to be punished!
(Heh heh... It went just as planned...)

(I was the one who shook the desk... and the item was
actually a cheap trinket...\I[12])
Master, do you need something from me?
Need? Have you forgotten about what happened recently?

You still haven't compensated for the valuable item you
damaged.
I received punishment as an apology for the damage...

That was punishment from an employer. Compensation for the
item is a separate matter.

It was an item with a warranty, so perhaps you should pay
this amount.
(Of course, this warranty is also a forgery.)
Such a large sum... I can't possibly pay...

It's not about whether you can or cannot pay. Compensation
is a matter of course.

If you truly don't have the money, shall I go directly to
your house to collect it?
Please, anything but that...! My husband is also at home...!

I will find a way...! So please, don't trouble my
husband...!
Hmm, even if you say that...
I beg of you...! I'll do anything that I can...!
Is that so? Well, I'm not a demon.

If you agree to do as I say, I might accept another form of
compensation.
And... what would that method be...?
Alecia has come to serve you.
Service, huh? That's a nice ring to it.

As a proud swordswoman, it seems you intend to honor our
contract.
Y-Yes... It's my responsibility for my blunder...
The cost for the broken item... I shall pay with my body...
That's fine\I[12]You seem to understand well\I[12]
Then without delay, Alecia, strip naked before me\I[12]

Can't you hear? Hurry up and take off your clothes, get

Surely you're not going to tell me you can't follow orders
so soon after agreeing?\I[12]
